\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Independent Institute of Education \'28IIE\'29 is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a Private Higher Education Institution and has programmes accredited by the CHE. \line \line \line The Institution is currently applying for the accreditation of a Higher Certificate in Communication Practices programme which will be offered in the distance mode of delivery at their Head Office - Sandton\'3A \line \line The Institution has also applied for the accreditation of the same programme to be offered in the contact mode of delivery which is still in process.\line \line The Institution is accredited to offer the following programmes\'3A \line - Diploma in Integrated Brand Communication \line - Bachelor of Arts in Corporate Communication \line - Higher Certificate in Journalism \line - Diploma in Journalism Studies \line - Bachelor of Arts Honours in Strategic Brand Communication\line - Bachelor of Arts in Strategic Brand Communication \line - Bachelor of Arts Honours in Communication\line \line The IIE has the following programmes that are HEQSF-Aligned and deemed Accredited\'3A \line - Diploma in Integrated Brand Communications \line - Bachelor of Arts in Corporate Communication \line - Bachelor of Arts in Creative Brand Communication \line - Bachelor of Arts Honours in Communications Management\cell \pard 

